    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《虫虫寓言：永恒之树苗》是一款冒险角色扮演游戏，玩家将跟随三位英雄——小薇、卡布和莱夫的脚步，踏上一场横跨虫之国的探险旅途，寻找传说中能赋予永生的秘宝「永恒树苗」。玩家将置身于色彩缤纷的虫虫世界，体验角色专属技能的巧妙搭配与多样化的地图探索。游戏的回合制战斗系统融入了可强化攻击的「动作指令」机制，让每一场战斗都充满策略性与节奏感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082710/extras/7d4c38129f72c6a219c13a8ce5166b76.poster.avif?t=1763638962\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082710/extras/7d4c38129f72c6a219c13a8ce5166b76.webm?t=1763638962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082710/extras/7d4c38129f72c6a219c13a8ce5166b76.mp4?t=1763638962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >广受好评并荣获Metacritic奖项的角色扮演游戏《虫虫寓言》现已推出免费1.2版本更新！全新任务、强力头目、升级版烹饪与冲刺系统，以及更多神秘内容等你发现！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082710/extras/4d4f4ce0ca5b99511c2ab6860dbc744e.poster.avif?t=1763638962\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082710/extras/4d4f4ce0ca5b99511c2ab6860dbc744e.webm?t=1763638962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082710/extras/4d4f4ce0ca5b99511c2ab6860dbc744e.mp4?t=1763638962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >背景故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在广袤丛林的深处，隐藏着一片小巧而繁荣的大陆——虫之国。来自世界各地的昆虫蜂拥而至，只为寻找传说中的宝藏。而其中最为神秘的，莫过于能赋予永生的珍宝——永恒树苗。据说只要尝上一片它的叶子，便能获得永生！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082710/extras/9c3df89f53a7af67da0225b9042b1d81.poster.avif?t=1763638962\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082710/extras/9c3df89f53a7af67da0225b9042b1d81.webm?t=1763638962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082710/extras/9c3df89f53a7af67da0225b9042b1d81.mp4?t=1763638962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为追寻这件远古秘宝，小薇、卡布与莱夫组成了一支勇敢的探险小队。你将跟随它们的步伐，穿越风格迥异的区域，破解谜题、击败强敌，帮助虫之国的居民解决难题，并揭开永恒树苗背后隐藏的终极秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >七大主线章节，带你踏遍虫之国的各个角落！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图探索与回合制战斗无缝衔接！灵活运用动作指令，使用小薇的蜂旋镖、卡布的犄角 、莱夫的冰魔法发动攻击或格挡敌人！利用回合接力机制，发挥团队协作，精准打击敌人弱点！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索特色地域：蚂蚁王国、险象环生的蛇口洞窟、风景如画的黄金山丘、迷失沙漠以及小薇的故乡蜜蜂王国！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借助烹饪系统将食材转化为助战道具！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验闲谈系统，聆听小队成员在发掘虫虫王国秘密时的趣味互动！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过30个支线任务与15个隐藏头目挑战！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082710/extras/624bf6bba3b862d15b05e7bde4fee094.poster.avif?t=1763638962\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082710/extras/624bf6bba3b862d15b05e7bde4fee094.webm?t=1763638962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1082710/extras/624bf6bba3b862d15b05e7bde4fee094.mp4?t=1763638962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
